trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Passado para exportadores e importadores WSDL personalizados para habilitar a personalização dos processos de exportação e importação de metadados de um ponto de extremidade WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext> class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=nameWithType> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext> classe representa o contexto no qual o WSDL personalizado para um ponto de extremidade ou é exportado usando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=nameWithType> ou importados usando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL:
trans-unit.target: As propriedades a seguir permitem recuperar o modelo de objeto do documento WSDL para o WSDL atual:

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=nameWithType> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=nameWithType> para o contrato de ponto de extremidade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=nameWithType> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=nameWithType> para o ponto de extremidade atual.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> propriedade obtém a associação para o ponto de extremidade atual.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> propriedade obtém a porta para o ponto de extremidade atual.

trans-unit.source: The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL:
trans-unit.target: Os métodos a seguir permitem que você adicionar ou remover elementos WSDL personalizados para os escopos apropriados no WSDL exportado ou importado:

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> método retorna a associação de falha para a falha específica.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> método retorna a falha para a associação de falha especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> método retorna a associação de mensagem para a mensagem especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> método retorna a mensagem para a associação de mensagem especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> método retorna a associação da operação para a operação especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> método retorna a operação para a associação da operação especificada.
